♪We were close♪

618
00:40:33,580 --> 00:40:34,850
♪We were distant♪

619
00:40:34,950 --> 00:40:35,950
♪Looking back♪

620
00:40:35,950 --> 00:40:37,560
♪At all that we’ve been through♪

621
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:39,780
♪All the more reason to be a flower♪

622
00:40:39,930 --> 00:40:42,100
♪Next life in spring♪

623
