♪Looking back♪

661
00:41:51,690 --> 00:41:53,290
♪At all that we’ve been through♪

662
00:41:53,290 --> 00:41:55,710
♪I’d be a flower in the next life♪

663
00:41:55,710 --> 00:41:57,710
♪So that I could be with you♪

664
00:41:57,710 --> 00:41:59,540
